Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:13.01,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:17.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 先輩のほうが早かった｡
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.39,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you got here first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:25.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水着 学校の更衣室で着てきたの｡
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I changed into my swimsuit \Nin the locker room at school.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.94,0:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got this dirty look in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩 目がｴﾛい｡
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.57,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ！\N(はしゃぎ声)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:47.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日まで ありがと｡
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
