Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし 泳ぐか｡
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, time to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:59.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 感想なし？
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No thoughts?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日まで ありがと｡
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise and shine, Onii-chan!{the new kyon-kun denwa}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:16.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん 朝ですよ｡
