Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら｡\Nあ…｡
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:43.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私はいいけど…｡
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I mind.
